name: Christmas Central
overview:
Dave’s Christmas Wonderland, is a division of Gordon Companies Inc, a family owned and operated business which was founded in 1977. Dave’s Christmas Wonderland is located at 2675 Union Road at William Street in Cheektowaga, NY 14227. 716-656-9540

Over the past 20 years Dave’s has become the leading Christmas store in Western New York. We carry one of the largest selections of Christmas merchandise, and our trees are decorated to perfection. Stop by any time to look at our gorgeous Christmas selection.
